<p>Hi {{ booking.name }},</p>
<p>This is confirmation from {{ shop.name }} that we have created a new booking for you.</p>
<p>You booked:</p>
<ul>
{% for item in booking.items %}
<li>{{ item.quantity }} x {{ item.product.title }} - {{ item.variant.title }}{% unless item.sku == blank %} (sku: {{ item.sku }}){% endunless %}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
<p>See you then!</p>
<p>{{ shop.name }}</p>